" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 485px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Peptic ulcers at low risk for rebleeding",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 465px; height: 217px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Ulcers with a clean base (panel A) or those with a flat pigmented red spot (panel B) are at low risk for rebleeding and do not need to be treated endoscopically.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
